<div class='toload lemma'>
<p><span class='envidentifier'>Lemma 1.2.47</span>
If $S$ is an inverse semigroup, $s,t\in S$, $s\land t$ exists and $z\leq t$, then $s\land z$ exists and $s\land z=(s\land t)z^*z$
</p>
</div>